title: Morning Glories (001 - 040) (2010 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Empire)
description:
Morning Glories (001 - 040) (2010 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Empire)


Morning Glory Academy is one of the most prestigious prep schools in the country... But behind it's hallowed doors something sinister and deadly lurks. When six brilliant but troubled new students arrive, they find themselves trapped and desperately seeking answers in a place where nothing is what it seems to be!

Publication History

Morning Glories is an ongoing creator-owned series written by Nick Spencer, published at Image comics' Shadowline imprint. In an interview with Comicvines' G-Man at the 2011 C2E2 Nick comments that this series is planned for 100 issues.
